{"tid":1508790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"係咪想TVB執笠呀？支那廉主演劇集，有大量「海馬床褥」植入廣告！","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:37:33.000Z","uid":267969,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"14e1a2392647a87f17cd7289175745e7f6cbfbef","tid":1508790,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪想TVB執笠呀？<br />\n唔該出少少力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n網民報料，今日翡翠台「她她她的少女時代」有大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>海馬床褥</strong></span>的置入式廣告<br />\n呢套劇其中一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>領銜主演係撐警嘅曹永廉</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>海馬床褥</strong>FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/seahorsemattress/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fseahorsemattress%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=40ed1f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/seahorsemattress/</a><br />\n<strong>Template，三擇其一</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望貴公司慎選宣傳渠道，例如XXXX (自己寫)，以保護品牌形象。本人不排除轉用替代產品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推介產品：</span></strong>金美夢，已經回覆抵制團隊完約檢討<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">意見收集：<br />\n大家想唔想每日或隔日去集中洗版？<br />\n一停洗版就多返廣告</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d5b53981b8369e43101a4b1a95e28882275447","tid":1508790,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:28:29.0